Interface CustomerAccountRepository

All Superinterfaces:
org.springframework.data.repository.CrudRepository<CustomerAccount,Long>, org.springframework.data.jpa.repository.JpaRepository<CustomerAccount,Long>, org.springframework.data.repository.ListCrudRepository<CustomerAccount,Long>, org.springframework.data.repository.ListPagingAndSortingRepository<CustomerAccount,Long>, org.springframework.data.repository.PagingAndSortingRepository<CustomerAccount,Long>, org.springframework.data.repository.query.QueryByExampleExecutor<CustomerAccount>, org.springframework.data.repository.Repository<CustomerAccount,Long>
@Repository public interface CustomerAccountRepository extends org.springframework.data.jpa.repository.JpaRepository<CustomerAccount,Long>
Repository interface for CustomerAccount entities. Extends JpaRepository to provide standard CRUD operations and query executions for CustomerAccount entities. This interface leverages Spring Data JPA to automatically generate implementations that handle the database operations required for managing CustomerAccount records, thereby reducing the need for explicit SQL.
